00:00:00.333 --> 00:00:01.133
madam

2
00:00:01.533 --> 00:00:02.900
Why don't you drink it?

3
00:00:03.900 --> 00:00:05.700
Jin Meiqi, don't go too far

4
00:00:07.733 --> 00:00:10.200
Madam, I was right

5
00:00:10.200 --> 00:00:11.533
You're not blind at all

6
00:00:11.533 --> 00:00:12.566
I guess so.

7
00:00:13.166 --> 00:00:14.900
I'm so disappointed in you.

8
00:00:15.266 --> 00:00:17.633
I didn't expect you to even lie to my husband

9
00:00:17.933 --> 00:00:20.166
I am the person closest to you

10
00:00:20.166 --> 00:00:21.900
You are even guarding against me

11
00:00:22.166 --> 00:00:25.533
Li Liangchen, you used to be the closest person to me

12
00:00:25.533 --> 00:00:27.066
But not anymore

13
00:00:27.066 --> 00:00:28.733
I thought my eyes would brighten again

14
00:00:28.733 --> 00:00:30.566
I can see my husband who loves me deeply

15
00:00:30.666 --> 00:00:33.166
I didn't expect to see a beast in clothes

16
00:00:33.166 --> 00:00:35.200
Hahaha late summer

17
00:00:35.533 --> 00:00:37.333
I didn't expect it to take so many years

18
00:00:37.333 --> 00:00:38.666
You are still so stupid

19
00:00:39.400 --> 00:00:41.300
Remember when I pursued you so hard

20
00:00:41.300 --> 00:00:44.133
A blind man cares for you in every way

21
00:00:44.133 --> 00:00:45.733
In order to be able to use you

22
00:00:45.733 --> 00:00:47.233
The world has leapt

23
00:00:47.333 --> 00:00:48.400
And here I am.

24
00:00:48.400 --> 00:00:49.666
I grew up poor

25
00:00:49.666 --> 00:00:52.566
Became the current president of the Xia Group

26
00:00:52.566 --> 00:00:56.300
Li Yangchen is my money to sponsor you to study abroad

27
00:00:56.400 --> 00:00:58.566
I left the company to you to manage

28
00:00:58.733 --> 00:01:01.600
You can become president not because you are capable

29
00:01:01.600 --> 00:01:03.066
But because of me

30
00:01:03.066 --> 00:01:04.833
Aren't you afraid of retribution?

31
00:01:05.566 --> 00:01:08.400
I only believe in money and power

32
00:01:08.400 --> 00:01:10.400
Bright hour, what are you doing?

33
00:01:10.400 --> 00:01:11.966
Do you still have the law in your eyes?

34
00:01:11.966 --> 00:01:14.100
When I get the next group

35
00:01:14.133 --> 00:01:16.466
I am the king

